Hardcore Pawn Chicago, Season 1, Episode 16.
Title: Comic Book Caper.

First aired on July 30, 2013.

Description: When a customer tries to sell her son's classic comic books, Wayne calls in an appraiser and sets up the shop for a double-cross. Then, a vintage fire truck ignites Randy's interest to make a deal. And later, will Wayne be able to save Royal from the appraiser's dirty dealing?

Note: web capture.
